title: Metallica 1983-91 AC3 5.1 Surround
description:
Recorded in AC3 5.1 Surround at 448kbps the same as a DVD movie 
   you buy from a shop or steal from ya mates house

Set up in a DVD folder for DVD Shrink or whatever you use to BURN
Has auto play from the first song
Has a DVD menu via your Remote for Album/song selection

1983 Kill 'em All
1984 Ride The Lightning
1986 Master of Puppets
1987 Garage Days Re-Revisited
1988 ...And Justice For All
1991 Metallica (Black Album)

    I only choose these albums lost interest after the black album..
                          
                            Sorry Headbangers
